org.apache.iceberg.types

Class FixupTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.iceberg.types.TypeUtil.CustomOrderSchemaVisitor<org.apache.iceberg.types.Type>
      • org.apache.iceberg.types.FixupTypes

  • public abstract class FixupTypes
extends org.apache.iceberg.types.TypeUtil.CustomOrderSchemaVisitor<org.apache.iceberg.types.Type>
    This is used to fix primitive types to match a table schema. This uses a reference schema to override types that were lost in round-trip conversion.
